| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4288 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b448a091-aeb8-582c-ab3d-7acd15c7f0b4"
